AA rogue: 130 DPS<br>
<br>
I'm anticipating that the AA rogue acquires improved weaponry along the way (a big assumption, I grant, but not an unreasonable one -- better weaponry needs to be accounted for somewhere). Note that all of the higher level figures assume Sebilis quality opponents (ie: no absurd AC).<br>
<br>
